metadata.name: Catch me up
metadata.description:
Lilly said, “I am your doll for today, are you going to catch me up?” The crane game or UFO catcher (UFO キャッチャー) is a concept to represented of NFT collector mind to grab a token in blockchain. This piece also reminding of my childhood life, and I think this will remind yours too.


Created: Q1 2022
Series: Moon Seeker Comics
